The paper discusses a method for automatically determining appropriate reviewers for a manuscript, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of a co-authorship network data structure suggests a focus on social network analysis (cs.SI) and the validation using referee bid data suggests a focus on databases (cs.DB) and systems and control (cs.SD).
